{"parse":{"title":"Optical Focus","pageid":411,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>2-1-125</b>\n</p><p>(Optical) Focus\n</p><p>The point on the axis of an optical system such that rays parallel to the axis and incident on the system converge to this point or appear to emanate from this point after refraction or reflection by the system.\n</p><p>(Figs. 12, 13, 14, 15, 17 and 19)\n</p><p><span class=\"mw-image-border\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:Ch2_Fig12.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/9/9b/Ch2_Fig12.jpg/400px-Ch2_Fig12.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"199\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/9/9b/Ch2_Fig12.jpg/600px-Ch2_Fig12.jpg 1.5x, /wiki/dictionary/images/9/9b/Ch2_Fig12.jpg 2x\"></a></span>\n</p><p><span class=\"mw-image-border\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:Ch2_Fig13.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/a/a2/Ch2_Fig13.jpg/400px-Ch2_Fig13.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"327\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/a/a2/Ch2_Fig13.jpg/600px-Ch2_Fig13.jpg 1.5x, /wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/a/a2/Ch2_Fig13.jpg/800px-Ch2_Fig13.jpg 2x\"></a></span>\n</p><p><span class=\"mw-image-border\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:Ch2_Fig14.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/f/fd/Ch2_Fig14.jpg/400px-Ch2_Fig14.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"303\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/f/fd/Ch2_Fig14.jpg/600px-Ch2_Fig14.jpg 1.5x, /wiki/dictionary/images/f/fd/Ch2_Fig14.jpg 2x\"></a></span>\n</p><p><span class=\"mw-image-border\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:Ch2_Fig15.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/8/84/Ch2_Fig15.jpg/400px-Ch2_Fig15.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"235\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/8/84/Ch2_Fig15.jpg/600px-Ch2_Fig15.jpg 1.5x, /wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/8/84/Ch2_Fig15.jpg/800px-Ch2_Fig15.jpg 2x\"></a></span>\n</p><p><span class=\"mw-image-border\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:Ch2_Fig17.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/b/b0/Ch2_Fig17.jpg/400px-Ch2_Fig17.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"232\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/b/b0/Ch2_Fig17.jpg/600px-Ch2_Fig17.jpg 1.5x, /wiki/dictionary/images/b/b0/Ch2_Fig17.jpg 2x\"></a></span>\n</p><p><span class=\"mw-image-border\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:Ch2_Fig19.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/f/f5/Ch2_Fig19.jpg/400px-Ch2_Fig19.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"400\" height=\"266\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/f/f5/Ch2_Fig19.jpg/600px-Ch2_Fig19.jpg 1.5x, /wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/f/f5/Ch2_Fig19.jpg/800px-Ch2_Fig19.jpg 2x\"></a></span>\n</p><p><br>\n</p><p><br>\n<br>\n<i>Please note that this is the term as it stands in the original <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\">IALA</span> Dictionary edition (1970-1989)</i>\n<br>\n</p>\n<div class=\"LanguageLinks\">\n<table width=\"100%\">\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\" style=\"background: #FFFFFF\">\n<td style=\"width: 25px; padding-left: 0em; border-right: 1px solid #aaaaaa;border-left: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-top: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-bottom: 1px solid #EEF3E2;\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:25px-Geographylogo.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\" title=\"Languages\"><img alt=\"Languages\" src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/8/82/25px-Geographylogo.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></td>\n<td style=\"padding: 1px 1em 0; background: #EEF3E2;\">\n<p><b><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">English</a></b>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>International Association of Marine Aids to Navigation and Lighthouse Authorities - AISM\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260615122743\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.066 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.081 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 60/1000000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 766/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 177/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/100\nExpensive parser function count: 4/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   16.973      1 -total\n 68.45%   11.618      1 Template:Languages\n 45.60%    7.740      4 Template:Languages/Lang\n 30.64%    5.200      1 Template:IALAFooter\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wiki_iala_dictionary_1_41:pcache:idhash:411-0!canonical and timestamp 20260615122743 and revision id 6545. Rendering was triggered because: page-view\n -->\n</div>"},"langlinks":[],"categories":[{"sortkey":"","*":"2.1_Optics_and_Vision"},{"sortkey":"","*":"Alphabetical_Index"},{"sortkey":"","*":"IALA_Dictionary_1970-89_Edition"}]}}